(144, 1, '2023-09-15 04:56:07', '2023-09-15 10:56:07', '', '377502858_636398448629459_4487669692955144611_n', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '377502858_636398448629459_4487669692955144611_n', '', '', '2023-09-15 04:56:07', '2023-09-15 10:56:07', '', 120, 'http://localhost/kamrun_diary/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/377502858_636398448629459_4487669692955144611_n.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(145, 1, '2023-09-15 04:56:14', '2023-09-15 10:56:14', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-144\" src=\"http://localhost/kamrun_diary/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/377502858_636398448629459_4487669692955144611_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"206\" height=\"206\" />\r\n\r\nA heart can\'t sound a lot\r\nBut it has a rhythmic rhyme\r\nIt could be swaying in gentle breeze\r\nSuddenly can transform into storm\r\nSo, never try to judge.\r\nA heart can be so soft\r\nJust like a bud\r\nStill in cloud there may have lightening\r\nBut in lightning\r\nEverything becomes crystal and clear\r\nSo, never do judge\r\nThe heart could be a fountain\r\nThe flow of stream\r\ncould be the rhythm of songs\r\nsometimes a colourful butterfly can fly\r\nThat\'s why still there is belonging chemistry\r\nNor physics or biology\r\nSo, a heart never be judged...\r\nA heart can\'t be erased\r\nBut can rewrite again and again\r\nEach time the new version is better than before\r\nIt\'s a god gifted award...\r\nSo, each time we need to bow down our head\r\nTo have a golden heart, such a beautiful gift ever.\r\nThe precious sign that is belonging in heart\r\nEach time it remembers me\r\nI am the best creature and I am the thy.', 'Golden Heart by Kamrun Nahar', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '120-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-09-15 04:56:14', '2023-09-15 10:56:14', '', 120, 'http://localhost/kamrun_diary/?p=145', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(146, 1, '2023-09-18 04:09:55', '2023-09-18 10:09:55', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-144\" src=\"http://localhost/kamrun_diary/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/377502858_636398448629459_4487669692955144611_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"206\" height=\"206\" />\n<blockquote>A heart can\'t sound a lot\nBut it has a rhythmic rhyme\nIt could be swaying in gentle breeze\nSuddenly can transform into storm\nSo, never try to judge.\n\nA heart can be so soft\nJust like a bud\nStill in cloud there may have lightening\nBut in lightning\nEverything becomes crystal and clear\nSo, never do judge\n\nThe heart could be a fountain\nThe flow of stream\ncould be the rhythm of songs\nsometimes a colourful butterfly can fly\nThat\'s why still there is belonging chemistry\nNor physics or biology\nSo, a heart never be judged...\nA heart can\'t be erased\nBut can rewrite again and again\nEach time the new version is better than before\nIt\'s a god gifted award...\nSo, each time we need to bow down our head\nTo have a golden heart, such a beautiful gift ever.\nThe precious sign that is belonging in heart\nEach time it remembers me\nI am the best creature and I am the thy.</blockquote>', 'Golden Heart by Kamrun Nahar', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '120-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-09-18 04:09:55', '2023-09-18 10:09:55', '', 120, 'http://localhost/kamrun_diary/?p=146', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(147, 1, '2023-09-15 05:00:11', '2023-09-15 11:00:11', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-144\" src=\"http://localhost/kamrun_diary/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/377502858_636398448629459_4487669692955144611_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"206\" height=\"206\" />\r\n<blockquote>A heart can\'t sound a lot\r\nBut it has a rhythmic rhyme\r\nIt could be swaying in gentle breeze\r\nSuddenly can transform into storm\r\nSo, never try to judge.\r\nA heart can be so soft\r\nJust like a bud\r\nStill in cloud there may have lightening\r\nBut in lightning\r\nEverything becomes crystal and clear\r\nSo, never do judge\r\nThe heart could be a fountain\r\nThe flow of stream\r\ncould be the rhythm of songs\r\nsometimes a colourful butterfly can fly\r\nThat\'s why still there is belonging chemistry\r\nNor physics or biology\r\nSo, a heart never be judged...\r\nA heart can\'t be erased\r\nBut can rewrite again and again\r\nEach time the new version is better than before\r\nIt\'s a god gifted award...\r\nSo, each time we need to bow down our head\r\nTo have a golden heart, such a beautiful gift ever.\r\nThe precious sign that is belonging in heart\r\nEach time it remembers me\r\nI am the best creature and I am the thy.</blockquote>', 'Golden Heart by Kamrun Nahar', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '120-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-09-15 05:00:11', '2023-09-15 11:00:11', '', 120, 'http://localhost/kamrun_diary/?p=147', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
